    "description": "<strong>Brain Show：你的团队中谁最聪明？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235150/extras/5a102449f274c66fdb22d0a7784a04a8.poster.avif?t=1768826328\" width=586 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235150/extras/5a102449f274c66fdb22d0a7784a04a8.webm?t=1768826328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235150/extras/5a102449f274c66fdb22d0a7784a04a8.mp4?t=1768826328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Brain Show</strong> 是一款智力问答游戏，带有一些搞笑但无害的幽默。沉浸在经典的游戏节目世界中：选择类别，回答问题，在各种挑战中淘汰对手，证明自己是团队中最聪明的！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235150/extras/0d589c333041a32e7ccdffa6c35d7a65.poster.avif?t=1768826328\" width=586 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235150/extras/0d589c333041a32e7ccdffa6c35d7a65.webm?t=1768826328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235150/extras/0d589c333041a32e7ccdffa6c35d7a65.mp4?t=1768826328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>每局最多支持 8 名玩家<br></li><li>超过 5,000 道题目，涵盖 41 个类别<br></li><li>13 种不同规则的比赛<br></li><li>富有魅力且幽默风趣（有点尴尬）的主持人评论你的表现<br></li><li>独特的机会，将你的好朋友变成一生的死敌！<br></li><li>支持在线多人游戏</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235150/extras/5ef1ea3ba1675507b220072e4949867e.poster.avif?t=1768826328\" width=586 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235150/extras/5ef1ea3ba1675507b220072e4949867e.webm?t=1768826328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235150/extras/5ef1ea3ba1675507b220072e4949867e.mp4?t=1768826328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Brain Show</strong> 的操作设计是基于我的吉娃娃和一只 22 岁的盲猫组成的测试组。所以，如果你的某些朋友从未玩过任何游戏，或者有人多喝了一杯，也不用担心。只需分发手柄，启动游戏，马上开始玩！无需说明书或解释！<br><br>参加电视节目，满足那些不好意思承认自己一直梦想参加的人！站上舞台，参与各种挑战，例如<strong>抢分</strong>或<strong>淘汰赛</strong>，在在线多人游戏中向朋友们展示谁是大师！<br><br>下载 <strong>Brain Show</strong> - 智力问答游戏并加入其中！",
